{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Two things about it-- one thing was that they would pin a, a, a label on her, in Japanese, so that when she started going out on her own, she could always be directed back.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she rather enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She was a woman in her 40s at the time, and she, you know, she was-- it was an adventure for her, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The other thing was, though, that she hadn't been able to get out until, until the passage from Japan to the west coast was paid for.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Up to Japan, she could pay for in German marks that she still had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The Japanese wanted American money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was no way of getting the $200 that he wanted to borrow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He had-- he came with debts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He owed my, my uncle, his, my mother's uncle money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He wanted to establish himself in this country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there was just nobody who would, who would lend him the, the money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he finally had to lower himself to the point where he asked a former suitor of my mother's who had been in the occupation army, the American occupation army in Mainz and had taken a shine to my mother before she was married.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But my mother remembered his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this man lived in Boston.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And my, my father-- actually, I don't know what it must have cost him to ask this man would he please, you know, lend him the money.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this man, after several correspondences, wrote back and said he had conferred with his friends, among whom was Ambassador Joseph Kennedy, about this problem.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they felt that it was not safe for a woman to travel alone through Russia and Siberia and Japan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they could not recommended it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
